  <brief_title>Preventative Delirium Protocol in Elderly Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Controlled Trial Reviewing the Effectiveness of a Preventative Delirium Protocol in Elderly Patients While Analyzing Its Consequential Effects on Awareness, PONV, and/or Pain Control</official_title>
  <sponsors>
